  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">About Me</h2>
    <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
      My Name is Mustafa Waheed Khan and I am a Software Developer, I have devoted myself towards polishing my skills in the field of Computer Sciences as well as any fields related to it. As a quick learner I can Quickly grasp on any task that comes my way. I am great at problem solving, which is the key fundament of programming and development. I have decent knowledge about digital marketing and SEO. I also have introductory understanding of graphic designing. Combining my Skills and Creativity I can put in the Hard work to get the job done.
       As a newbie Elixir and Erlang developer passionate about building scalable, fault-tolerant systems
      and real-time web applications. With a deep interest in functional programming, I focus on
      creating clean, maintainable code that stands the test of time.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-300">
      I am currently pursuing my degree at the <span class="font-semibold">University of Central Punjab</span>
      with a current CGPA of <span class="font-bold text-indigo-300">3.81</span>.
    </p>
  </section>

